%% Data Flow Diagram - Distributed Workloads
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Test Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrainOp as Training Operator<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workers as Worker Pods<br/>GPU Compute
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>6379/TCP GCS
    participant RayWorkers as Ray Workers<br/>10001/TCP Object Store
    participant RayDash as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Distributed PyTorch Training Job (Kueue-managed)
    User->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob + LocalQueue<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload admission event
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload (quota check)<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: PyTorchJob unsuspend event
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    Workers->>Workers: NCCL/RDMA inter-node<br/>dynamic/TCP, plaintext
    Workers->>S3: Download dataset (MNIST)<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS credentials
    Workers->>Workers: GPU Training Compute
    Workers->>S3: Upload trained model<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS credentials

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Ray Cluster Job Submission
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster/RayJob<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: RayCluster event
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Head + Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    User->>RayDash: POST /api/jobs/<br/>HTTP/8265, no auth
    RayHead->>RayWorkers: Task distribution<br/>TCP/6379 GCS, plaintext
    RayWorkers->>RayHead: Results<br/>TCP/10001 Object Store, plaintext
    User->>RayDash: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP/8265, no auth
    RayDash-->>User: Job status + logs

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Kubeflow Trainer v2 TrainJob
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: TrainJob event (ClusterTrainingRuntime)
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create training Pods<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    Workers->>Workers: Distributed training<br/>NCCL, plaintext
    Workers->>S3: Model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS credentials
